{"tid":1608564,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"荃灣青年疑中實彈重傷　證實為荃灣何傳耀中學中五學生 大批朋友到醫院 有人情緒激動","createTime":"2019-10-01T10:46:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T10:53:32.000Z","uid":133680,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5f15f618ef188945466a302f9edd131006f57f5e","tid":1608564,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:46:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483672-20191001.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483672-20191001.htm&d=6oYmF1jQM6ZNNDbF9Ucscd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=d6b55c32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483672-20191001.htm&h=04379e7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483672-20191001.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n荃灣大河道一名青年懷疑中實彈槍受重傷，他的朋友證實傷者是荃灣公立何傳耀紀念中學一名中五男生，傷者的一班朋友到瑪嘉烈醫院了解情況，他們情緒激動，有人落淚。<br />\n<br />\n事發下午4時許，男傷者在荃灣大河道中槍後倒地，左邊心口流血，網上片段看到，傷者倒在地上後大叫「心口好痛」，要求送院。警方消息證實，事發現場開過實彈槍。"},{"pid":"534c409531886d3edaaaac42ed1203f2b667b351","tid":1608564,"uid":174907,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5f15f618ef188945466a302f9edd131006f57f5e","tid":1608564,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:46:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483672-20191001.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483672-20191001.htm&d=6oYmF1jQM6ZNNDbF9Ucscd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=d6b55c32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483672-20191001.htm&h=04379e7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483672-20191001.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n荃灣大河道一名青年懷疑中實彈槍受重傷，他的朋友證實傷者是荃灣公立何傳耀紀念中學一名中五男生，傷者的一班朋友到瑪嘉烈醫院了解情況，他們情緒激動，有人落淚。<br />\n<br />\n事發下午4時許，男傷者在荃灣大河道中槍後倒地，左邊心口流血，網上片段看到，傷者倒在地上後